The article is a statement from an individual sending greetings to Muslims observing the holy month of Ramadan. It highlights the significance of Ramadan, which commemorates the revelation of the sacred Quran to Muhammad. During this month, Muslims fast from dawn to dusk, recite passages from the Quran, and engage in charitable acts. The statement emphasizes the importance of inward reflection, spiritual renewal, and prayer during Ramadan, as well as fostering a sense of unity and fellowship with others. The individual, along with Melania, extends their best wishes to Muslims in the United States and worldwide for a blessed month of celebration.